Member Function Documentation

template<typename T, XsArrayDescriptor const & D, typename I>
template<ptrdiff_t F, typename R, typename Derived>
difference_type XsArrayImpl< T, D, I >::IteratorImplBase< F, R, Derived >::operator- ( const this_type &  other) const
inline

Returns the difference in number of items between the two iterators.

The function computes the difference between this iterator and other. The difference may be negative if other is 'ahead' of this. The function takes the direction of the iterator into consideration.

Parameters
otherThe iterator to subtract from this.
Returns
The difference between the two iterators.
